modName: Neo - Lei Fang and Christie -CBBEv3M by Nausicaa
summary:
This is conversion of "Neo - Lei Fang and Christie" in oblivion mod.
Original author is Neovinci aka Meister.

This Mod has 2 Female Costumes, with 'Lei Fang' and 'Christie' in a Japanese Video Game "Dead or Alive"
descriptionHtml:
[b][i] [size=14]Introduction[/size][/i][/b]

I can't speak english well.

This is conversion of "Neo - Lei Fang and Christie" in oblivion mod.
Original author is Neovinci aka Meister.

[color=yellow]Neo permitted to me it conversion.[/color]

Original link : [url=http://oblivion.nexusmods.com/mods/38955]http://oblivion.nexusmods.com/mods/38955[/url]

-------------------------------------- original information -------------------------------------------
This Mod has 2 Female Costumes, with 'Lei Fang' and 'Christie' in a Japanese Video Game "Dead or Alive"

but I still have not played "DOA".
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

[b][i] [size=14]Description[/size][/i][/b]

[img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/26826-1-1352813518.jpg[/img]

[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/26826-2-1352813171.jpg[/img]

[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/26826-3-1352813171.jpg[/img]

Here is armor, glove, boots & garter belt.

It is craftable & smithing at Daedric, DragonScale.
Garter belt is craftable at jewelry.

Lei Fang's armor is DragonScale.
Christie's armor is Daedric.

This is CBBEv3M base.
It is compatible CBBE3. (If you are CBBE3 user, you will use it without CBBEv3M body.)

[color=red]Caution.[/color]
[color=red]My skyrim version is 1.8.151. I made a esp file with newest CK.[/color]
[color=red]If your version is lower than 1.8, you have nothing in craft list.[/color]
[color=red]You must update new version.[/color]
